OL,3,CCharity calls for action as 210,000
OL,4,CScottish children found to be food
OL,5,Cinsecure
OL,7,FA leading charity has called for
OL,8,Faction after research found 210,000
OL,9,Fchildren in Scotland live in food
OL,10,Finsecure households.
OL,12,FThe Trussell Trust urged the Scottish
OL,13,FGovernment to increase the level of
OL,14,Fits flagship Scottish child payment,
OL,15,Fas well as follow through its
OL,16,Fcommitment to mitigate the two-child
OL,17,Flimit and provide cash for those
OL,18,Fwaiting for their first universal
OL,19,Fcredit payments.
