OL,3,CCharity calls for action as 210,000
OL,4,CScottish children found to be food
OL,5,Cinsecure
OL,7,FThe call comes as the charity found
OL,8,F15% of households ` equivalent to one
OL,9,Fmillion people and 210,000 children `
OL,10,Fin Scotland are food insecure.
OL,12,FThe figure represents a slight
OL,13,Fdecrease from 17% in 2022, with the
OL,14,Fcharity suggesting there is "emerging
OL,15,Fsigns of some progress" north of the
OL,16,Fborder.
