OL,5,Cinsecure
OL,7,FThe research ` which was conducted
OL,8,Fthrough a survey carried out in the
OL,9,Fsummer of last year and released on
OL,10,FWednesday ` also found 5% of all
OL,11,Fhouseholds sought charitable help for
OL,12,Ffood insecurity.
OL,14,FTrussell defines food insecurity as
OL,15,Fthose cutting back on the quantity or
OL,16,Fquality of food due to a lack of money.
