OL,4,CScottish children found to be food
OL,5,Cinsecure
OL,7,FThe charity's report said: "Next
OL,8,Fyear's elections are an opportunity to
OL,9,Freflect collectively on how to put the
OL,10,Fbuilding blocks in place here in
OL,11,FScotland to ensure everyone has enough
OL,12,Fmoney to afford the essentials ` and
OL,13,Fno-one needs to access support through
OL,14,Fcharitable food providers.
OL,16,F"While the UK Government holds
OL,17,Fsignificant responsibilities, there is
OL,18,Fstill much the Scottish Government can
OL,19,Fdo to deliver a tangible reduction in
OL,20,Ffood bank need.
OL,26,@oD@\OUxD@AOU
