OL,4,CScottish children found to be food
OL,5,Cinsecure
OL,7,F"This report illustrates two
OL,8,Finescapable facts relating to these
OL,9,Fcommitments: First, that hunger and
OL,10,Ffood bank need are driven by multiple
OL,11,Ffactors, requiring a cross-government
OL,12,Fapproach to this commitment.
OL,14,F"Second, that there can be no serious
OL,15,Fpathway to ending the need for
OL,16,Femergency food without investing in
OL,17,Ffurther updates to our social security
OL,18,Fsystem in Scotland."
