OL,3,CCharity calls for action as 210,000
OL,4,CScottish children found to be food
OL,5,Cinsecure
OL,7,FThe report urged the Scottish
OL,8,FGovernment to increase the Scottish
OL,9,Fchild payment benefit to #40 per week
OL,10,Ffrom its current rate of #27.15,
OL,11,Fclaiming it would lift 84,000 people
OL,12,Fout of hunger and hardship and bring
OL,13,Fmore than #400 million in economic
OL,14,Fbenefits.
OL,16,FMitigating the two-child limit ` which
OL,17,Fstops certain benefits being available
OL,18,Fto families with more than two
OL,19,Fchildren ` would bring in #115 million
OL,20,Fin economic benefits and help 27,000
OL,21,Fstruggling people, the report claimed.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/10
