OL,7,FProviding a grant for people forced to
OL,8,Fwait five weeks for their first
OL,9,Funiversal credit payment would help
OL,10,F6,000 people, the charity added.
OL,12,FSocial Justice Secretary Shirley-Anne
OL,13,FSomerville said: "Too many families
OL,14,Fare struggling to make ends meet as a
OL,15,Fresult of Brexit and the UK cost-of-
OL,16,Fliving crisis ` that is why we are
OL,17,Ftaking action on child poverty, which
OL,18,Fhas fallen in Scotland in contrast to
OL,19,Fthe rest of the UK.
