OL,3,CCharity calls for action as 210,000
OL,4,CScottish children found to be food
OL,5,Cinsecure
OL,7,F"A report published last week showed
OL,8,Fthat our policies are helping more
OL,9,Ffamilies avoid the use of food banks
OL,10,Fand to have healthy meals, while
OL,11,Freducing food insecurity.
OL,13,F"But I remain focused on doing
OL,14,Feverything we can to support those who
OL,15,Fneed help, including by effectively
OL,16,Fscrapping the two-child limit at the
OL,17,Fstart of 2026, which is set to benefit
OL,18,F43,000 children next year, with our
OL,19,Fmodelling estimating that 20,000 fewer
OL,20,Fchildren will live in relative poverty.
OL,26,@oD@AOUuD@AOU
