OL,5,Cinsecure
OL,7,F"And Universal Credit has been too low
OL,8,Ffor too long, so I repeat the call on
OL,9,Fthe UK Government to introduce an
OL,10,Fessentials guarantee, ensuring that
OL,11,Fsocial security benefits adequately
OL,12,Fcover the cost of food and other
OL,13,Fessentials and better protect people
OL,14,Ffrom the impacts of poverty."
